{"tid":466492,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有一見鍾情記得好好把握","createTime":"2017-11-12T15:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T15:33:42.000Z","uid":139381,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a18f682fd2924e803cfbb435dd82f23e4a633cdf","tid":466492,"uid":139381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:15:36.000Z","msg":"嗰日返緊車展幫手遞酒<br />\n留意到個女仔係我身邊盤旋左好耐<br />\n跟住佢怕怕醜醜咁走過黎問我d酒係咪可以拎<br />\n個下我覺得佢勁可愛,有種一見鍾情嘅感覺<br />\n跟住兩次佢都走過黎問我 撩我講野<br />\n佢唔算好靚，行行下仲自己會傻笑<br />\n但佢嗰種傻傻地嘅感覺搞到我想一直保護佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後見到佢我尷尬病發作無視左佢:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住佢就走左喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我連佢咩名電話都唔知<br />\n呢幾日佢係我腦海中盤旋左好耐<br />\n就算發夢都見到佢，成世仔未試過呢種感覺<br />\n之後幾日專登返去都撞唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵盡ig fb 打卡地點一齊方法都搵唔番佢<br />\n奉勸巴絲遇到一見鍾情唔理3721記得要把握 唔好好似我咁撚on9<br />\n會後悔好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"9b07589ce4925207fa6b82347f135aa0f64f30ec","tid":466492,"uid":10374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:20:14.000Z","msg":"ff少陣"},{"pid":"c4ef076c0261f7bbfb877b4d2ed209152894cad0","tid":466492,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:25:59.000Z","msg":"啱 上次無問個七日鮮攞contact 後悔到依家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62987d460ed0dac934443cd57818eb1665f259bf","tid":466492,"uid":139381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ff少陣</blockquote><br />\n收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b5df2b2775952dc0f04b0e4f5a71df254a6d1a","tid":466492,"uid":139381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱 上次無問個七日鮮攞contact 後悔到依家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm